Select an item from the drop-down control and click the '''Add''' button to create a new [http://wiki.wontology.org/wiki/help.php?title=Help:GlossaryAtoO#anchor_Connection connection] for the current [http://wiki.wontology.org/wiki/help.php?title=Help:GlossaryAtoO#anchor_Item item].  You have to click '''Add''' after making a selection in order for it to be stored.  Each '''Add''' button is independent, and only saves the information it is immediately associated with; you cannot fill in multiple connection-creation controls and then save them all with a single '''Add'''.
